  "texts": [
    "While this technique enables efficient data representation, it compromises model accuracy.",
    "To counteract this, H-FL incorporates a bias correction mechanism that is activated prior to each FL training round on the client side.",
    "It is designed to adjust the gradients of features affected by the lossy compression.",
    "This corrector comprises of multiple fully connected layers, which are sequentially arranged and whose parameters are dynamically updated based on the SVD outcomes of the features extracted from the initial, shallow model layers.FedOBD [51] segments a large model into semantic blocks.",
    "It enables FL server and clients to selectively exchange quantized blocks."
  ],
